Last.fm allows a [[User]] to _love a [[Track]]
Spotify allows the [[User]] to _create a [[Playlist]]

This application will allow you to add your Last.fm loved Tracks to a Spotify Playlist.

This may happen at a certain frequency, i.e. Monthly, and have a customisable Playlist name.

Refs

https://developer.spotify.com/en/libspotify/docs/examples.html

http://last.fm/api

LovedTracks: http://www.last.fm/api/show?service=329
